                <p>Get assistance anytime with our dedicated support team available 24/7.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <i class="fas fa-id-badge text-red-400 text-3xl mb-4"></i>
